<div id="imageContentfc06fd0e003a499ca163e61a4864eae5">
</div>
<p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;">A free Park &amp; free Ride scheme for hospital staff, patients and visitors </span></span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;">runs between Doncaster Racecourse, Car Park 'A' on Leger Way, Doncaster and DRI, Gate 3, (Outpatients &amp; Emergency entrances) Monday - Friday (excluding Bank Holidays) between 6.30am and 10.00 pm. T</span></span>he bus journey normally takes <strong>7 - 10 minutes</strong>. Please allow adequate time to park your vehicle and ride up to the hospital in good time for your appointment.</p>
